properties.name: Marine Hill
properties.description: Posted by Jtaylo63The area we called Marine Hill was where I lived in Guantanamo Bay, Cuba for 2 years for 4th and 5th grade. The marker is on the house that I lived in. The hill consisted of the major Marines that lived on base, including the CO and XO of the Marines on the island. The CO lived in that huge house and had all the land and dock with it. His son, two other guys and I used to always go boating and fishing out on the bay. Cuba was an awesome place to live.
